// === CONTEXTS (where bindings apply) ===
// Workspace              - Global workspace level
// Editor                 - Any editor pane
// Editor && vim_mode == normal/insert/visual - Vim mode specific
// Terminal              - Terminal panel
// ProjectPanel          - File explorer
// AgentPanel            - Claude/AI panel
// GitPanel              - Git panel
// Picker                - Fuzzy finder dialogs
// BufferSearchBar       - Find/replace bar
