//
// === MAIN ACTION GROUPS ===
// editor::              - Text editing (Cut, Paste, Format, Rename, etc)
// workspace::           - Window/workspace (Save, NewFile, ToggleZoom, etc)
// pane::                - Tab/pane management (Split, Close, Navigate)
// agent::               - Claude AI (Chat, ToggleFocus, NewThread, etc)
// git::                 - Git operations (Stage, Commit, Blame, Restore)
// project_panel::       - File explorer (NewFile, Rename, Delete, etc)
// terminal_panel::      - Terminal (Toggle, Clear, etc)
// file_finder::         - Fuzzy file search
// project_search::      - Project-wide search
// buffer_search::       - Current file search
// diagnostics::         - Errors/warnings panel
// outline::             - Symbol outline
// vim::                 - Vim-specific actions
// theme_selector::      - Theme picker
// command_palette::     - Command palette
// language_selector::   - Language mode selector
//
// === VIM NOTES ===
// - Space is configured as leader key
// - ; opens command palette in normal mode
